 +Appr 		!!= * **@CODE@**:  Approximative numeral –ļ–į—Ą—ā–į-–ļ–ĺ–Ľ–ľ–į, –ļ–ĺ–Ľ–ľ–ĺ—ą–ļ–į "two or three" requires split?
 +AssocColl !!= * **@CODE@**:  -ne- ; avide-; -–ľ–Ķ—Ā—ā—Ć
 +Coll 		!!= * **@CODE@**:  Collective
 +Card 		!!= * **@CODE@**:  cardinal
