!!
!! Verb voice:
 +Act 	!!= * **@CODE@**:  active
 +Pss 	!!= * **@CODE@**:  passive
!!
!! Verb moods are:
 +Cond 	!!= * **@CODE@**:  conditional –Ĺ–ī—Ź—Ä—Ź- protasis
 +NegCnd !!= * **@CODE@**:  negative conditional –ě—Ą—ā—Ź—Ä—Ź- negative protasis
 +NegCndSub !!= * **@CODE@**:  negative conditional –ě—Ą—ā—Ź—Ä—Ź–Ľ—Ć negative protasis
 +Conj 	!!= * **@CODE@**:  conjunctional "–ě–Ľ—Ć"
 +Des 	!!= * **@CODE@**:  desiderative –ļ—Ā–ĺ–Ľ—Ć "was about to; wanted to"
 +Ind 	!!= * **@CODE@**:  indicative
 +Imprt !!= * **@CODE@**:  imperative
 +Opt 	!!= * **@CODE@**:  optative
 +Prec  !!= * **@CODE@**:  Precative mood is a directive mood that signals that the utterance is a request. imperative + additional vowel and cons -–į–ļ–į forms equal Precative

!! Verb tenses are
 +Prs 	!!= @CODE@ present and future ! nominal	conjugation as well
 +Prt1 	!!= @CODE@ preterite I ! only finite verbal
 +Prt2 	!!= @CODE@ preterite II ! nominal conjugation as well

