! List of spurious lexica
! These should be fixed.


! This lexicon would allow a loop whereby any full form
! could be treated as a noun
! E.G. –ľ–Ķ–∑–Ķ—Ź–ļ # 'anything'
! E.G. –ľ–Ķ–∑–Ķ—Ź–ļ+–ĺ—Ā—Ć # 'This _anything_ you are talking about'
!LEXICON Encapsulate


!LEXICON ADV-SUPERL
!+Adv+Superl: # ;


!LEXICON TESTINGTESTING
!
!–ę–ī–∂—č–ī TESTCOMP ;
!—Ā–ł–Ĺ TESTCOMP ;
!–ĺ—Ą–ł—Ü–ł–į–Ľ TESTCOMP ;
!—Ä–į–ī–ł–ĺ–į–ļ—ā–ł–≤ TESTCOMP ;
!
!LEXICON TESTCOMP
!
!+CmpTest: # ;


